Setup notes
-----------

Diagram:

					    Node pool
					  +--------+
					  | Node 0 |
  +----------+       +-------------+      +---------+
  | Launcher | <---> | Coordinator | <---> | Node 1 |
  +----------+       +-------------+       +---------+
			  /   \             | Node N |
			 /     \            +--------+
			/       \
		       /         \
		    mail      database stats

(1) The user tsuite runs as must have sudo privileges.
(2) ssh keys must be set up on each machine for the user to ssh to the
    local machine as well as from the launching node.

